citation: Proclamation under the Health Practitioner Regulation National Law (Tasmania) Act 2010 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Health Practitioner Regulation National Law (Tasmania) Act 2010

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2(1) of the Health Practitioner Regulation National Law (Tasmania) Act 2010 fix 1 July 2010 as the day on which the provisions of that Act, other than sections 9 and 11 , commence.

28 June 2010

PETER G. UNDERWOOD

Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

MICHELLE O'BYRNE

Minister for Health

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 30 June 2010

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Health and Human Services.
